name: TheCrazyCouponChickBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Get a list of available coupons from The Crazy Coupon Chick daily using your voice. If you are interested in a coupon, you can quickly get to it by clicking on it in the Alexa app Activity screen.

All the coupons are curated from the website https://thecrazycouponchick.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
